-Graffy, Driz Ro <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugolgi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Golgi</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.graffe.com/spells/purple_gate.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/11/01 9:24:09 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.facelink.com/edit/raw/rawimage/70/1333570.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Don't Buy IT!</span><hr size=1> I don't understand why people are refusing to purchase them.  Do you not have any friends in the game that might need a TL once in a while? <p><Base target=_blank>
