60 Sorcerer<BR>
Midnight Sun<BR>
Ayonae Ro</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uderal.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Deral</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/11/01 12:49:27 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: One port I want...</span><hr size=1> As I ranger I feel for you wizards with Verants Horse hockey attempt to make your class more feasible.  Speaking as another &quot;not wanted&quot; class I can only say that I think the translocate spells are great for meleers but you all really get the shaft on the deal.  Unfortunately the Vision (TM) has struck again.  I have and will support giving the wizard class an offense upgrade.  It is my belief that Verant fears a group of wizards killing the &quot;big&quot; mobs and exp hunting in an all wizard group.  I say let it happen because in the end it takes well balanced groups to accomplish the big things.  So you can get to 60 faster thats fine but you will still need the meleers to help kill those Uber mobs.<br>
<br>
